  "detailed_description": "<h1>EXPLORE THE MIND OF THE ODDGOD IN THIS FREE EXPANSION!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/ec8e52f6d45d127e1738a17e4b9c8f5f.avif?t=1770126036\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras_big/ec8e52f6d45d127e1738a17e4b9c8f5f.avif?t=1770126036 width=800 height=218 /></span></p></p><br><h1>Become Part of the Community!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/6b0999d0dd3e49d62c644c04faf4b59f.avif?t=1770126036\" width=616 height=220 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/0e69c4f0773e2cc1d194002d7cb989ec.poster.avif?t=1770126036\" width=616 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/0e69c4f0773e2cc1d194002d7cb989ec.webm?t=1770126036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/0e69c4f0773e2cc1d194002d7cb989ec.mp4?t=1770126036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A HAND-DRAWN METROIDVANIA WITH BRANCHING STORYLINES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you explore the Realm of Aestik, you will need to make impactful decisions which will alter the course of the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Platform your way through this strangely unique world and fathom the mysterious corruption that drives sane creatures mad.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight off wild beasts and navigate through harsh environments to uncover the world's interconnected maps and secrets. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLORE THE REALM OF AESTIK</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Vast, Interconnected World:</strong> Traverse the intricate maps of Aestik, discovering hidden secrets and unraveling the mysteries of the realm.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Environments:</strong> Every corner of Aestik offers something new, from the cozy Bubblewoods to the spooky Gourd Glade.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/3b6c0ef2f940bf91b92c4c9b17b70165.poster.avif?t=1770126036\" width=616 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/3b6c0ef2f940bf91b92c4c9b17b70165.webm?t=1770126036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/3b6c0ef2f940bf91b92c4c9b17b70165.mp4?t=1770126036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>NAVIGATE THE REALM</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenging Obstacles:</strong> Overcome demanding platforming challenges with precision and skill.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customize Your Playstyle:</strong> Equip ability runes that fit your personal playstyle to navigate through the world!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/4574b0a2ceb5ab3c15c85a40671e57e6.poster.avif?t=1770126036\" width=616 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/4574b0a2ceb5ab3c15c85a40671e57e6.webm?t=1770126036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/4574b0a2ceb5ab3c15c85a40671e57e6.mp4?t=1770126036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>STAND AGAINST YOUR FOES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Snappy Combat:</strong> Engage in fast-paced combat against over 25 unique foes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Epic Boss Battles:</strong> Face off against more than 15 formidable bosses that will test your combat prowess and strategy.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/61534081067ca13edf9c1e32b376f01a.poster.avif?t=1770126036\" width=616 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/61534081067ca13edf9c1e32b376f01a.webm?t=1770126036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/61534081067ca13edf9c1e32b376f01a.mp4?t=1770126036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHOOSE YOUR FATE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Impactful Choices:</strong> Your decisions will alter the course of your adventure & lead to unique encounters!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Replayability:</strong> Experience different outcomes and storylines based on the paths you choose.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/8aa19028f306ac33a3bb45a16606a77b.poster.avif?t=1770126036\" width=616 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/8aa19028f306ac33a3bb45a16606a77b.webm?t=1770126036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199330/extras/8aa19028f306ac33a3bb45a16606a77b.mp4?t=1770126036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ADDITIONAL FEATURES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgrade Paths:</strong> Find potions that let you choose from different permanent upgrades!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Anthology:</strong> Discover all the lifeforms of the Realm of Aestik, filling the pages of this comprehensive guide!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mysterious Portals:</strong> Enter portals scattered around the world & complete their trials to collect valuable Fragments!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Followers:</strong> Find cute little creatures and take them with you on your journey!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Secluded Ponds:</strong> Take a break and go fishing with Bradlae!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenge Mode:</strong> Tackle trials outside of the main game!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Assist Options:</strong> Customize settings to make the game more accessible, providing support for overcoming challenging sections and enhancing your gameplay experience!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
